  "title": "Sales Manager (HORECA)",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Achieve company sales targets and drive revenue growth</p></li><li><p>Develop new markets, customers, and key accounts</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain strong customer relationships</p></li><li><p>Lead, train, and motivate the sales team</p></li><li><p>Develop sales strategies based on products and market conditions</p></li><li><p>Secure and manage sales contracts</p></li><li><p>Prepare sales reports and updates for management</p></li><li><p>Handle customer issues, urgent requests, and feedback promptly</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with internal departments on sales matters</p></li><li><p>Any other adhoc duties as assigned<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Min 4-5 years experience in Food & Beverage/Hospitality Industry</p></li><li><p>Possess own car</p></li><li><p>Location: Loyang</p></li><li><p>Working Hours: Mon - Fri (8.30am - 5.45pm), Sat (8.30am - 2.30pm, once every 4 weeks)</p></li><li><p>Salary: Up to $4500 (Basic) + Transport Allowance + Commission<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>How to apply:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants kindly state your expected salary, last drawn salary and starting date.</p><p>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Log on to www.e-cruitteam.com.sg for more job opportunities!<br /></p><p>EA Personnel: Teo Kai Xin, Joey</p><p>EA Reg ID: R23114229</p><p>EA Licence No.:19C9603</p>",
